title: Estonia Gross Household Saving Rate
description: Household Saving Rate in Estonia decreased to 10.54 percent in 2021 from 14.32 percent in 2020. Personal Savings in Estonia averaged 7.17 percent from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 19.19 percent in 1995 and a record low of -3.86 percent in 2004. This page provides - Estonia Gross Household Saving Rate - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
